data.description: This home boasts a spacious open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a dedicated study. Enjoy the elegance of quartz countertops in the generously sized kitchen and bathrooms, along with gas cooking and bamboo flooring. Say goodbye to carpet downstairs with plantation shutters adorning every window. Unwind in the master bath's jetted tub, while upstairs, a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom awaits. The ample backyard offers potential for a private pool oasis. Residents can conveniently access Sonterra's club amenities via golf cart, including golf, tennis, dining, and social gatherings. The property is equipped with two recently replaced indoor AC units and a new water heater, ensuring comfort and efficiency. Come make this little gem your today!
